'''Brassvines''' were [[Plant/Legends|plants]] that grew on [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]]. The plants were named for the large, dull-[[Gold/Legends|gold]] thorns that grew from their vines. These thorns were almost as hard as [[Durasteel/Legends|durasteel]], and were eaten by [[grasser]]s.

Once stripped of thorns, brassvines could be made into serviceable ropes, which the [[Korun/Legends|Korunnai]] often used them for this purpose. They were also used as nails.

